      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted mt-4">VRC costs 40-60% less than a comparable freight elevator when factoring in equipment, installation, pit, machine room, and code compliance. See <a href="/resources/conveyor-cost-guide/" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-hover font-semibold">cost guide</a>.</p>
